## Interface: 30300
## Title: CleanLoot
## Notes: Clean, ElvUI-inspired reskin of the group loot roll frames (Need/Greed/Disenchant/Pass). Standalone, no ElvUI required. Movable, stack direction, quality-colored borders, roll tooltips, optional popup skipping.
## Notes-frFR: Reskin epure des fenetres de loot roll (Need/Greed/Disenchant/Pass), inspire d'ElvUI. Autonome, sans ElvUI. Repositionnable, direction d'empilement, bordures colorees par qualite, tooltips de roll, popups optionnellement ignorees.
